# Spirebound Game Roadmap

Welcome to the official roadmap for Spirebound! This document outlines planned features, improvements, and milestones for the development of this mini web game.

---

## 🟢 Current Status

- Core repository files set up: README, LICENSE, .gitignore
- Game concept and basic structure defined

---

## 🛠️ In Progress

- Initial playable prototype
- Basic game loop (start, play, end)
- Character creation system

---

## 📝 Short-Term Goals (v0.1–v0.2)

- Implement character creation UI and logic
- Basic environment and map rendering
- Simple enemy AI and encounters
- Health and stats system
- Inventory system (basic items)
- Game UI polish (menus, buttons, feedback)

---

## 🚀 Mid-Term Goals (v0.3–v0.5)

- Multiple character classes and skills
- Advanced enemy types and boss encounters
- Save/load game state functionality
- Sound and music integration
- Mobile responsiveness and accessibility improvements
- Tutorial and help screens

---

## 🎯 Long-Term Goals (v1.0+)

- Story mode and quest system
- Multiplayer or leaderboard features
- Expanded inventory and crafting system
- Achievements and progression tracking
- Richer animations and effects
- Community feedback and mod support

---

## 🗓️ Timeline (Tentative)

| Milestone             | ETA          | Description                                  |
|-----------------------|--------------|----------------------------------------------|
| Playable Prototype    | Month 1      | Basic game loop, character creation          |
| Content Expansion     | Month 2-3    | Enemies, items, environments                 |
| Polish & Features     | Month 4-5    | UI, sound, saving/loading, tutorials         |
| Beta Release          | Month 6      | Full gameplay loop, feedback integration     |
| v1.0 Launch           | Month 7+     | Feature complete, bug fixes, documentation   |

